WEBVTT

00:01:56.931 --> 00:02:00.421
Tana suv ta'minotini 
to'ldirgandan so'ng, matritsa ochilib,

00:02:00.421 --> 00:02:03.887
zarar ko'rmagan, tirik 
hujayralarni bo'shatadi.

00:02:03.887 --> 00:02:08.151
Qurg'oqchilikdan tashqari, imildoqlar 
boshqa to'siqlarni ham yenga oladi:

00:02:08.151 --> 00:02:09.416
ularni muzlatish,

00:02:09.416 --> 00:02:11.830
suv qaynaydigan haroratda 
qizdirish, kuchli

00:02:11.830 --> 00:02:13.507
radiatsiya bilan nurlantirish

00:02:13.507 --> 00:02:17.092
va hatto kosmosdagi vakuumga 
joylashtirish mumkin.

00:02:17.092 --> 00:02:19.221
Bu xususiyat imildoq
o'zga sayyoraga mansub

00:02:19.221 --> 00:02:22.562
mavjudot, degan xato taxminlarning 
paydo bo'lishiga olib kelgan.

00:02:22.562 --> 00:02:24.150
Bu fikr qiziq eshitilishi mumkin,

00:02:24.150 --> 00:02:27.751
ammo fanda imildoqlar Yerda 
paydo bo'lib, asta-sekin rivojlanib

00:02:27.751 --> 00:02:29.772
borganligi haqida
dalillar mavjud.

00:02:29.772 --> 00:02:32.503
Evolyutsiya jarayonida 
imildoqlarning 1100 dan ortiq turi